OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776731804
OL,3,CKeir Starmer to face second bruising
OL,4,Cday in Parliament over Mandelson
OL,5,Cscandal
OL,7,FSir Keir Starmer is to face another
OL,8,Fbruising day in Parliament over the
OL,9,Fscandal surrounding Lord Peter
OL,10,FMandelson's appointment as US
OL,11,Fambassador.
OL,13,FSir Olly Robbins will have a chance to
OL,14,Frespond to the Prime Minister, who
OL,15,Fblamed the sacked senior civil servant
OL,16,Ffor "deliberately" keeping him in the
OL,17,Fdark over Lord Mandelson's failure to
OL,18,Fpass security vetting checks before
OL,19,Ftaking the Washington DC posting.
OL,26,@xD@EOUxD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
