PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776731804
OL,3,CKeir Starmer to face second bruising
OL,4,Cday in Parliament over Mandelson
OL,5,Cscandal
OL,7,FThe House of Commons will subject the
OL,8,FPrime Minister's latest efforts to lay
OL,9,Fout the facts of the scandal to
OL,10,Ffurther scrutiny on Tuesday, as MPs
OL,11,Fhold an emergency debate on Lord
OL,12,FMandelson's appointment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776731804
OL,3,CKeir Starmer to face second bruising
OL,4,Cday in Parliament over Mandelson
OL,5,Cscandal
OL,7,FSir Olly, until last week the most
OL,8,Fsenior civil servant in the Foreign
OL,9,FOffice, will reportedly tell the
OL,10,FForeign Affairs Committee that the
OL,11,FGovernment pressured him into clearing
OL,12,FLord Mandelson, despite the peer's
OL,13,Frelationship with paedophile financier
OL,14,FJeffrey Epstein, and business links to
OL,15,FRussia and China.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776731804
OL,3,CKeir Starmer to face second bruising
OL,4,Cday in Parliament over Mandelson
OL,5,Cscandal
OL,7,FLord Mandelson, who spent nine months
OL,8,Fas US ambassador before fresh details
OL,9,Fof his relationship with Epstein
OL,10,Femerged, was a political appointment
OL,11,Fto the plum diplomatic role, rather
OL,12,Fthan the Washington job going to a
OL,13,Fcareer diplomat.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776731804
OL,3,CKeir Starmer to face second bruising
OL,4,Cday in Parliament over Mandelson
OL,5,Cscandal
OL,7,FThe Times also reported that Sir Olly
OL,8,Fwill use his "box office" appearance
OL,9,Fat the committee to reveal he did not
OL,10,Fsee the formal recommendation by
OL,11,Fvetting officials that Lord Mandelson
OL,12,Fshould not be given clearance, while
OL,13,Finsisting the UK Security Vetting
OL,14,F(UKSV) process is only advisory.
OL,16,FOn Monday, the Prime Minister said he
OL,17,Fchallenged Sir Olly over why he went
OL,18,Fagainst the recommendation of UKSV.
OL,26,@pD@NOUpD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
