OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776731804
OL,3,CKeir Starmer to face second bruising
OL,4,Cday in Parliament over Mandelson
OL,5,Cscandal
OL,7,F"I did ask him and I didn't accept his
OL,8,Fexplanation," Sir Keir told the
OL,9,FCommons. "That's why I sacked him."
OL,11,FThe Prime Minister also said he would
OL,12,Fnot have appointed Lord Mandelson if
OL,13,Fhe had known the peer had failed the
OL,14,Fchecks and insisted there was no
OL,15,Fpressure from No 10 to push through
OL,16,Fthe high-profile appointment.
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@MO]qD@JOUqD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
