OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776731804
OL,3,CKeir Starmer to face second bruising
OL,4,Cday in Parliament over Mandelson
OL,5,Cscandal
OL,7,FConservative leader Kemi Badenoch
OL,8,Fapplied for the emergency Commons
OL,9,Fdebate about the scandal, telling MPs
OL,10,Fit was "a matter of national security
OL,11,Fbecause the Prime Minister has
OL,12,Fadmitted appointing a known serious
OL,13,Fsecurity risk to our most sensitive
OL,14,Fdiplomatic post".
OL,16,FIt is not known which minister will
OL,17,Fappear at the debate on behalf of the
OL,18,FGovernment.
OL,26,@rD@HOUvD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
