FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776731804
OL,3,CKeir Starmer to face second bruising
OL,4,Cday in Parliament over Mandelson
OL,5,Cscandal
OL,7,FThe Guardian reported that the
OL,8,FIntelligence and Security Committee, a
OL,9,Fcross-party group of parliamentarians
OL,10,Fwhich scrutinises matters of security,
OL,11,Fhas received vetting documents
OL,12,Frelating to Lord Mandelson.
OL,14,FThe peer was flagged as "high concern"
OL,15,Fby UKSV and it was recommended that
OL,16,Fclearance should be denied to him, the
OL,17,FGuardian reported.
OL,26,@vD@YOUvD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
