OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776731804
OL,3,CKeir Starmer to face second bruising
OL,4,Cday in Parliament over Mandelson
OL,5,Cscandal
OL,7,FSir Keir said in his appearance in the
OL,8,FCommons on Monday afternoon that the
OL,9,FGovernment was investigating security
OL,10,Fconcerns relating to Lord Mandelson's
OL,11,Ftime as US ambassador.
OL,13,FHe also said the terms of a probe into
OL,14,FGovernment security vetting have been
OL,15,Fupdated in light of the latest
OL,16,Frevelations about Lord Mandelson and
OL,17,Fthe inquiry will be led by Sir Adrian
OL,18,FFulford, a senior judge and chairman
OL,19,Fof the Southport Inquiry.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/9
